      <description><![CDATA[<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C4vU6uzrVSy/"><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/503084270_1030521842554925_5846616292442032202_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_s640x640_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=109&amp;ig_cache_key=MzMyNzk3MDY0NjU2OTA3OTk4Ng%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjcyMHgxMjgwLnNkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=Oerg4QBBpwUQ7kNvwEfZDe6&amp;_nc_oc=AdoLBYLAU4X2AxcArR3G3gwnvUC72Ot9uLeOCNU7GRPDTcgCT1LLNPnsBM3NnJqOjW0&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=YPrbAZM53ixcyHDUS6dKsw&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyIccwXi_y2QLW2enRsrUHnmQ56Cj3DCKN-eAxMesTtKg&amp;oe=69CA28A8" alt="Video-thumbnail fra @presstube" /></a></p><p><strong>🎬 Video</strong></p><p><strong>@presstube</strong></p><p>Presstube.com/sit (Link in bio)<br/>
<br/>
Every day I sit in silent meditation for one hour at 5am EDT / 9am GMT.<br/>
<br/>
Meditating with other people is one of my favorite things. If you also like the idea of sitting in community and are looking to connect with other enthusiastic meditators, jump in!<br/>
<br/>
A one hour sit can be a lot if you’re not used to it. So feel free to join half way through for 30 minutes, or even pop in for just the last 5, 10 or 15 minutes. Start small, enjoy yourself and build up gradually.<br/>
<br/>
The zoom typically stays open for ~15m after the sit for anyone who feels like sharing or talking shop. However, there is ZERO pressure to stick around or say a single word. It is fully kosher to drop off the zoom without even saying goodbye. Sometimes maintaining early morning or post-sit peace and quiet is important.<br/>
<br/>
This is a lurker, introvert, hermit and quiet person friendly zone.<br/>
<br/>
